post_text:
Check out our latest newsletter, with information including:

- a message from Superintendent Nancy House with important updates including information about plans to salute the class of 2020;

- a link to a survey the Board of Education is conducting to gather feedback from parents and residents regarding their thoughts on the search for a new Superintendent;

- a story about what distance learning has looked like for our students;

- and Milford Eagle images you can download for your student to color.

Click here to see it: https://myemail.constantcontact.com/Milford-Schools-Eagle-eNews---April-2020.html?soid=1115188962904&aid=G1rPbWNsHLs

